l-group pi-horizontal-group-no-labels\">\n\t<caption class=\"pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-secondary-background pi-item-spacing\">Chapter Chronology</caption>\n\t\n\t<tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\">← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_58\" title=\"Chapter 58\">Previous</a></td>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_60\" title=\"Chapter 60\">Next</a> →</td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n</p><p><b>Chapter 59</b> is titled \"Obligation\".\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Cover_Page\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cover Page</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Short_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Short Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Long_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Long Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quick_Reference\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quick Reference</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Chapter_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chapter Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Characters\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Author_Comment\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Author Comment</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Site_Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Site Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cover_Page\">Cover Page</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_59%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Buggy%27s_Crew_Adventure_Chronicles\" title=\"Buggy&#39;s Crew Adventure Chronicles\">Buggy's Crew Adventure Chronicles</a>, Vol. 18: \"Explosion!! Sleepwalking Richie\".\n</p><p>Still dreaming of adventures as captain of his own crew, a sleepwalking <a href=\"/wiki/Richie\" title=\"Richie\">Richie</a> unknowingly knocks out <a href=\"/wiki/Mohji\" title=\"Mohji\">Mohji</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Cabaji\" title=\"Cabaji\">Cabaji</a> both.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Short_Summary\">Short Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_59%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In order to save <a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a>'s life, <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> decides to destroy the <a href=\"/wiki/Baratie\" title=\"Baratie\">Baratie</a>. While they are arguing, <a href=\"/wiki/Pearl\" title=\"Pearl\">Pearl</a> attacks them but <a href=\"/wiki/Gin\" title=\"Gin\">Gin</a> knocks him out as he wants to kill Sanji himself.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Long_Summary\">Long Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_59%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a> continues to let <a href=\"/wiki/Pearl\" title=\"Pearl\">Pearl</a> assault him as he has decided to die rather than let the <a href=\"/wiki/Baratie\" title=\"Baratie\">Baratie</a> be taken by the <a href=\"/wiki/Krieg_Pirates\" title=\"Krieg Pirates\">Krieg Pirates</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> becomes angry as he does not understand how Sanji's death would repay <a href=\"/wiki/Zeff\" title=\"Zeff\">Zeff</a>'s sacrifice. To put an end to Sanji's suicide, he destroys the Baratie since it is the target of <a href=\"/wiki/Krieg\" title=\"Krieg\">Don Krieg</a>. While Sanji and Luffy fighting about the best solution to save Zeff, Pearl decides to attack them. However, he is stopped by <a href=\"/wiki/Gin\" title=\"Gin\">Gin</a>, who defeats him with one blow. He proclaims he will take care of Sanji's death, personally.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quick_Reference\">Quick Reference</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_59%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapter_Notes\">Chapter Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_59%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Luffy destroys most of the <a href=\"/wiki/Baratie\" title=\"Baratie\">Baratie</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Gin\" title=\"Gin\">Gin</a> defeats <a href=\"/wiki/Pearl\" title=\"Pearl\">Pearl</a> so he can kill <a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a>.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_59%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D6&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table class=\"CharTable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/Pirate\" title=\"Pirate\">Pirates</a>\n</th>\n<th>Citizens\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Monkey D. Luffy</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Buggy_Pirates\" title=\"Buggy Pirates\">Buggy Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Mohji\" title=\"Mohji\">Mohji</a> (cover)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Richie\" title=\"Richie\">Richie</a> (cover)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Cabaji\" title=\"Cabaji\">Cabaji</a> (cover)</li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Krieg_Pirates\" title=\"Krieg Pirates\">Krieg Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Krieg\" title=\"Krieg\">Krieg</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Gin\" title=\"Gin\">Gin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Pearl\" title=\"Pearl\">Pearl</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Red_Hair_Pirates\" title=\"Red Hair Pirates\">Red Hair Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Shanks\" title=\"Shanks\">Shanks</a> (flashback)</li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Baratie\" title=\"Baratie\">Baratie</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Zeff\" title=\"Zeff\">Zeff</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Patty\" title=\"Patty\">Patty</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Carne\" title=\"Carne\">Carne</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Author_Comment\">Author Comment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_59%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><br />\n</p><table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: center; width:50%\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">Author Comment</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:90%\"><div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Translation\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Translation</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Original\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Original</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p><br />\nI bought an Akiko Wada album. SHE IS THE SOOOWL-SHOUTIN' SINGER! She shouts from her SOOOWL**.</p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p><br />\nワダアキコのアルバム買った。ディスイズタマスィーシャウトシンガーだ。タマスィーの叫びだ。</p></div></div>—<a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\">Eiichiro Oda</a></td><td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/a/ad/Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20230801133230\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Eiichiro Oda WSJ Avatar.png\" data-image-key=\"Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"><i>English translation by <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" clas