      "*": "{{Chapter Box\n| title = Obligation\n| image = \n| jname = 恩\n| rname = On\n| ename = Sanji's Debt\n}}\n\n'''Chapter 59''' is titled \"Obligation\".\n\n==Cover Page==\n[[Buggy's Crew Adventure Chronicles]], Vol. 18: \"Explosion!! Sleepwalking Richie\".\n\nStill dreaming of adventures as captain of his own crew, a sleepwalking [[Richie]] unknowingly knocks out [[Mohji]] and [[Cabaji]] both.\n\n==Short Summary==\nIn order to save [[Sanji]]'s life, [[Monkey D. Luffy|Luffy]] decides to destroy the [[Baratie]]. While they are arguing, [[Pearl]] attacks them but [[Gin]] knocks him out as he wants to kill Sanji himself.\n\n==Long Summary==\n[[Sanji]] continues to let [[Pearl]] assault him as he has decided to die rather than let the [[Baratie]] be taken by the [[Krieg Pirates]]. [[Monkey D. Luffy|Luffy]] becomes angry as he does not understand how Sanji's death would repay [[Zeff]]'s sacrifice. To put an end to Sanji's suicide, he destroys the Baratie since it is the target of [[Krieg|Don Krieg]]. While Sanji and Luffy fighting about the best solution to save Zeff, Pearl decides to attack them. However, he is stopped by [[Gin]], who defeats him with one blow. He proclaims he will take care of Sanji's death, personally.\n\n==Quick Reference==\n===Chapter Notes===\n*Luffy destroys most of the [[Baratie]].\n*[[Gin]] defeats [[Pearl]] so he can kill [[Sanji]].\n\n===Characters===\n{| class=\"CharTable\"\n!colspan=\"2\"| [[Pirate]]s\n! Citizens\n|-\n|\n;[[Straw Hat Pirates]]\n*[[Monkey D. Luffy]]\n----\n;[[Buggy Pirates]]\n*[[Mohji]] (cover)\n*[[Richie]] (cover)\n*[[Cabaji]] (cover)\n|\n;[[Krieg Pirates]]\n*[[Krieg]]\n*[[Gin]]\n*[[Pearl]]\n----\n;[[Red Hair Pirates]]\n*[[Shanks]] (flashback)\n|\n;[[Baratie]]\n*[[Zeff]]\n*[[Sanji]]\n*[[Patty]]\n*[[Carne]]\n|}\n\n==Author Comment==\n{{WSJ Comment}}\n\n==Site Navigation==\n{{Baratie Arc}}\n{{Buggy's Crew Adventure Chronicles}}\n[[ca:Capítol 59]]\n[[de:On]]\n[[it:Capitolo 59]]\n[[fr:Chapitre 59]]"
